\sum_{k=1}^n k^3 = \left(\frac{1}{2}n(n+1) \right)^2
(\frac{n}{2}(n+1))^2 + (n+1)^3
(n+1)^3
(n+1)(n+1)^2
(n+1)^2
(n+1)^2((\frac{n}{2})^2 + (n+1))
(n+1)^2((\frac{n}{2})^2 + (n+1))=(n+1)^2\frac{n^2+4n+4}{4}=(n+1)^2\frac{(n+2)^2}{2^2}= \left(\frac{1}{2}(n+1)((n+1)+1) \right)^2
